<%- layout("layout/boilerplate.ejs") %>
<link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">


<main class="main about-page">
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="about-hero" aria-label="About MentorMap hero">
    <div class="hero-inner" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="800">
      <h1>About MentorMap</h1>
      <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        MentorMap is a transformative platform designed to connect school students with bright, passionate university mentors in their local area.
        We believe that learning is most impactful when it’s personal, relatable, and driven by fresh knowledge. By bridging the gap between generations
        of learners, we aim to cultivate a supportive educational ecosystem where young students gain confidence, clarity, and care from mentors who
        understand their academic journey. With every connection made, MentorMap empowers communities, encourages curiosity, and builds a stronger
        foundation for future success.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT CARDS -->
  <div class="about-container">
    <article class="about-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>To build a strong learning bridge between university students and school children, delivering knowledge, care, and support locally.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="about-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
      <h2>Why MentorMap?</h2>
      <p>We believe that fresh knowledge and close-age mentorship can make a real impact on school students. Our platform helps parents find motivated university students nearby who can teach with understanding and energy.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="about-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>We are a team of passionate developers and educators aiming to create meaningful connections in the education space. MentorMap is not just a website — it’s a mission to make quality tutoring accessible and personal.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</main>

<script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>
<script> AOS.init(); </script>
